You do it like this, it'll open up in a fire,

9
00:01:03,011 --> 00:01:06,139
you'll get burned and die.

10
00:01:06,215 --> 00:01:08,342
[Fire Bell]

11
00:01:08,417 --> 00:01:09,941
Let's go!

12
00:01:10,018 --> 00:01:12,452
What d'you got, Adcox, a big deal?

13
00:01:12,521 --> 00:01:14,455
Medium deal, Captain.

14
00:01:14,523 --> 00:01:16,889
Hey, Brian, want to come along?

15
00:01:16,959 --> 00:01:19,757
- Dad...
- Stephen, you've come a dozen times.

16
00:01:19,828 --> 00:01:22,319
Give your brother a chance. What d'you say?

17
00:01:22,397 --> 00:01:24,422
We'll be back in a minute. How about it?

18
00:01:24,500 --> 00:01:26,331
- Sure!
- Come on!

19
00:01:36,812 --> 00:01:40,077
