- [Horn Blast]

20
00:01:40,148 --> 00:01:42,480
1545 Idylwild.

21
00:01:42,551 --> 00:01:45,486
[Siren]

22
00:01:57,266 --> 00:01:59,291
- Give it a yank, a good pull.
- [Horn Blast]

23
00:01:59,368 --> 00:02:01,893
You've gotta get these cars outta the way.

24
00:02:01,970 --> 00:02:04,336
- Give it another yank!
- [Horn Blast]

